ch\u2014Supplies moderate: demand\nmoderate; market steady. Nearby Mary\nland, bushel baskets. Savoy type, 75e.\nOranges\u2014Supplies moderate: demand\nmoderate; market steady. California,\nboxes. Navels No. 1, 170's and smaller,\n8808.50; 150\u2019s, 87.5008; 123\u2019s, 3\u00abO\n25.\nGrapefruit\u2014Supplies light: demand\nlight; market steady, Florida, boxes.\nNo. 1. medium size, 8805-50; large\nHze. 85.5005; No. 2, medium else,\n35.5005.75; large size, 34.50 05.\n1886\u20141930\n44 Year* of Constant\nProgress\nSTOCKETTALK NO. 4\nThis is our Story and we\u2019re\nGoing to Stick to it!\nMove to Larger\nQuarters\nThe phenomenal pre war\ngrowth of our business necessi\ntated larger quarters, eo, in\n1916 we moved into our pres\nen plant constructed especially\nfor us. A modern, fireproof\nbuilding of 8 stories and a\nbasement totaling 19,400 square\nfeet of floor space given over\nentirely to the manufacture\nand sale of office equipment\nand supplies.\nThis Is the largest establish\nment in Washington devoted\nexclusively to \u201cOffice Service.\"\nWe Want Your Business!\nram\n27","height":"30445","width":"24329"}}
